    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The process of ageing",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 3.12,
      "endTime": 11.65
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is one of the most unpleasant discoveries we make about ourselves as we get older?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 11.66,
      "endTime": 20.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "At the age of twelve years, the human body is at its most vigorous.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.55,
      "endTime": 26.84,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It has yet to reach its full size and strength, and its owner his or her full intelligence: but at this age the likelihood of death is least.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.85,
      "endTime": 39.38,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Earlier, we were infants and young children, and consequently more vulnerable;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.39,
      "endTime": 47.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Young",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "年轻的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "later, we shall undergo a progressive loss of our vigour and resistance which, though imperceptible at first",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 47.25,
      "endTime": 56.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "will finally become so steep that we can live no longer,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.61,
      "endTime": 61.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "however well we look after ourselves, and however well society, and our doctors, look after us.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.71,
      "endTime": 70.09,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Look",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "看"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "This decline in vigour with the passing of time is called ageing.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.1,
      "endTime": 75.33,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It is one of the most unpleasant discoveries which we all make that we must decline in this way, that if we escape wars,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.34,
      "endTime": 85.34,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "accidents and diseases we shall eventually 'die of old age', and that this happens at a rate which differs little from person to person,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 85.35,
      "endTime": 96.89,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "so that there are heavy odds in favour of our dying between the ages of 65 and 80.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 96.9,
      "endTime": 104.67,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Some of us will die sooner, a few will live longer -- on into a ninth or tenth decade.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 104.68,
      "endTime": 112.88,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But the chances are against it,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.89,
      "endTime": 115.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and there is a virtual limit on how long we can hope to remain alive, however lucky and robust we are.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 115.45,
      "endTime": 123.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "How",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "怎样，如何"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Normal people tend to forget this process unless and until they are reminded of it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 123.88,
      "endTime": 130.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We are so familiar with the fact that man ages, that people have for years assumed that the process of losing vigour with time,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 130.41,
      "endTime": 139.47,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "of becoming more likely to die the older we get, was something self-evident",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.48,
      "endTime": 145.36
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "like the cooling of a hot kettle or the wearing-out of a pair of shoes.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 145.37,
      "endTime": 150.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Hot",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "热的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They have also assumed that all animals,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 150.73,
      "endTime": 154.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and probably other organisms such as trees, or even the universe itself, must in the nature of things 'wear out'.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 154.17,
      "endTime": 164.81,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Most animals we commonly observe do in fact age as we do,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 164.82,
      "endTime": 169.81,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "if given the chance to live long enough;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 169.82,
      "endTime": 172.41
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and mechanical systems like a wound watch, or the sun,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 172.42,
      "endTime": 177.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "do in fact run out of energy in accordance with the second law of thermodynamics (whether the whole universe does so is a moot point at present).",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 177.54,
      "endTime": 189.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But these are not analogous to what happens when man ages.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 189.17,
      "endTime": 194.67,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A run-down watch is still a watch and can be rewound.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 194.68,
      "endTime": 199.88,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "An old watch, by contrast, becomes so worn and unreliable that it eventually is not worth mending.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 199.89,
      "endTime": 209.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But a watch could never repair itself--it does not consist of living parts, only of metal, which wears away by friction.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 209.98,
      "endTime": 220.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We could, at one time, repair ourselves--well enough, at least, to overcome all but the most instantly fatal illnesses and accidents.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 220.98,
      "endTime": 233.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Between twelve and eighty years we gradually lose this power;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 233.69,
      "endTime": 239.71,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "an illness which at 12 would knock us over, at 80 can knock us out, and into our grave.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 239.72,
      "endTime": 248.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If we could stay as vigorous as we are at twelve,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 248.79,
      "endTime": 252.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "it would take about 700 years for half of us to die, and another 700 for the survivors to be reduced by half again.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 252.54,
      "endTime": 257.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
